for your glory and for the profit of the body.

00:47:48.860 --> 00:47:50.860
I pray, Lord, that you would use us.

00:47:50.860 --> 00:47:54.860
I pray that you would help us, Lord, to be surrendered and yielded to thee.

00:47:54.860 --> 00:47:57.860
I pray that in the moment of invitation that you'd have your will and way.

00:47:57.860 --> 00:47:59.860
For it's in Christ's name we pray.

00:47:59.860 --> 00:48:00.860
Amen.

00:48:00.860 --> 00:48:01.860
Would you stand with me?

00:48:01.860 --> 00:48:02.860
Heads are bowed, eyes are closed.

00:48:02.860 --> 00:48:03.860
Kimberly's going to play quietly on the piano.

